<h2 id="download" style="text-align:center;border-bottom:none;padding-bottom:0">Download Sonic Velocity</h2>

The <strong>Beta Demo 1.0.3</strong> includes a hub world, a test stage for practicing mechanics, the full Frostfall Act 1 level, and a boss fight against Eggman with in-engine cutscenes. Both keyboard and controller are supported, with haptic vibration on compatible gamepads.

